| Booking v1 API | `Huz-Backend/booking/api_urls.py`, `Huz-Backend/booking/views/api_v1.py` | DRF booking endpoints under `/api/v1` | 5 v1 endpoints; 3 consumed by FE |
| Management Domain | `Huz-Backend/management` | Super-admin approvals, payment transfer, reporting/KPI, hotel master catalog | 24 endpoints; 9 consumed by FE |
| Chat Domain | `Huz-Backend/chat` | REST chat inbox/message endpoints + websocket routing | 5 REST endpoints; 0 consumed by current FE API literals |
| Web App Shell | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src` | Public site, booking flow, user settings UI | Routing in `src/routes/AppRoutes.jsx`; current route tree exposes 43 routes (`28` public/auth, `15` protected or alias routes) |
